{"tid":1472968,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★深水埗警署一帶，曾是全港最大的戰俘集中營","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:45:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d391bcee346d380983c0114785167e93d326102","tid":1472968,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"現時的西九龍中心，以及鄰近的深水埗公園、麗閣邨等，都是昔日1928年英軍所駐守的深水埗軍營範圍，現今還有三塊「軍部地界」石碑留作紀念。隨住三年零八個月的到來，此處亦成為了日軍用作收押7000名英、加和印藉士兵的戰俘營。不少戰俘因抵受不住酷刑而在營中去世，此處是全港最大的戰俘營，腳氣病、痢疾和白喉等惡疾非常猖獗，死傷無數。單是1942年，就有數百名戰俘因此死去。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日，鬧鬼的傳聞還有不少人提起，在我們看來是空無一人的街道，或許警方用獨特的視角看到千軍萬馬的生命能量呢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/discoverhongkongheritage/photos/a.397829117306744/727087804380872/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdiscoverhongkongheritage%2Fphotos%2Fa.397829117306744%2F727087804380872%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXP7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=3dd26dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/discoverhongkongheritage/photos/a.397829117306744/727087804380872/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"5ea315341f87427c0542ac54f7fcfb4810c126da","tid":1472968,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c581970c3f9eb01652f24689872694260f8d30de","tid":1472968,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n816拎錢行動X英美港盟集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n818民陣遊行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiENHnW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiENHnW.png&h=0871cd00&s={SIZE}\"